{
  "text": "Since the DDSLL style is developed as a countermeasure against power analysis attacks [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , special care has to be taken while designing the NMOS trees, especially since large NMOS trees can be used to implement complex functions with even three or four inputs in order to save area.",
